Purpose: This folder contains all Adapter classes. Adapters are responsible for populating data into RecyclerView or other components like ViewPager. They bind the data to the views in the UI.

What to include:

* Custom adapter classes for RecyclerView, ViewPager, etc.
* Logic to bind data to view holders or specific views

Examples:

* HeroAdapter.kt
* InventoryAdapter.kt
* GalleryAdapter.kt

== Example [InventoryAdapter.kt]
    // imports
    class InventoryAdapter(private val listInventory:MutableList<Inventory>,
                           private val navController: NavController)
                           :RecyclerView.Adapter<InventoryViewHolder>()
                           {
        override fun onCreateViewHolder(parent: ViewGroup, viewType: Int): InventoryViewHolder {
            val binding = ItemInventoryBinding.inflate(LayoutInflater.from(parent.context),parent, false)
            return InventoryViewHolder(binding, navController)
        }
        override fun getItemCount(): Int {
            return listInventory.size
        }
        override fun onBindViewHolder(holder: InventoryViewHolder, position: Int) {
            val inventory = listInventory[position]
            holder.setItemInventory(inventory)
        }
    }